---

## 6. Risks & Mitigation

### 6.1 Insufficient Test Coverage
- Require at least one test per PR.  
- Reviewers verify test relevance and coverage.

### 6.2 Backend Changes Breaking Frontend
- Maintain integration tests for critical commands.  
- Update mocks and test cases when API changes.

### 6.3 Manual Testing Gaps
- Maintain a consistent manual testing checklist.  
- Perform full manual testing at the end of each sprint.

